To run this example run, in a shell of two different hosts:
(remember changing the .connect(Container) in pupil.asl to the 
name of the container where the agent teacher runs)

*********HOST 1*****

erl -pa ../../eJason/ebin/ -name TeacherContainer

Then start agent teacher with ejason:pcr(teacher).


*********HOSTS N*****

erl -pa ../../eJason/ebin/ -name PupilContainer

Then start different pupils  with ejason:pcr(pupil).







